" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本歌有d係唔齊，一係就唔知係咪鎖區，見到隻歌個名係度，但暗左色禁落去播唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:聽歐美韓國多，所以會繼續用spotify<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96277283be442126f13c97f45681058093bb061","tid":2017103,"uid":50894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:05:25.000Z","msg":"市面上既聽歌app除左joox我都用過<br />\n最鍾意係moov，因為音質高，缺點係外國歌少<br />\n而家都係用緊spotify<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d177a2bfd0ff2bbe32c6f24ac8351b03f7a3d59","tid":2017103,"uid":15511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:12:28.000Z","msg":"spotify"},{"pid":"7bdc624f8fd8825e4610d76627a74d65b3711fa6","tid":2017103,"uid":59322,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"KKBOX歌最齊 好多都係得佢一間exclusive 以為得台灣歌係假象"},{"pid":"cd1d2ddd4cb9f11233b7de0a767d0524ad897beb","tid":2017103,"uid":6446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:26:55.000Z","msg":"spotify冇歌詞"},{"pid":"236f67abba56fbae6c54206ce408eb3cb1e232b9","tid":2017103,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:36:51.000Z","msg":"Spotify更新左睡眠時間"},{"pid":"9bab072b23e4c8a614ad4c8970e4714cd8509a54","tid":2017103,"uid":318430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"我都係聽日本歌 Apple music, 絕對係三者之中最齊。不過我用日本App Store，唔知會唔會有分別， Apple Music 用返自己iPhone個 music app，所以可以同本身手機裏面嘅音樂用返同一個app，有時候如果Apple Music 1你想聽嘅日本歌，可以喺iTunes買，買完可以入返落去Music app度，又或者上網自己諗渠道下載又得，又係用返同一個app。音質方面就KK box應該係最好320K MP3 ， Apple Music 256 AAC，但係iPhone用任何藍牙傳輸都係用返AAC，所以音質冇分別"},{"pid":"2f38e7eab019a5264cae25461004718b19defc48","tid":2017103,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a46dcda4acab05defcd750d